(Photo: Evan Vucci, AP, File)Hughes won’t get another pay check until mid-May and her husband’s relief payment has yet to arrive.
The one-time relief payments will offset some of the economic shock of the health crisis, said Mark Zandi, chief economist at Moody’s Analytics.